= Rogueliki - A Roguelike Wiki =

This is a pre-alpha release. You can check in the following way.

== For web use ==
  # upload lib, locale, wiki and rogueliki.html (and wiki.php for save)
  # access rogueliki.html (or rogueliki.html#XMLRPC)

== For local use ==
  # access rogueliki.html (or rogueliki.html#TiddlyWiki.Files)

----
== Hash Access ==

(files:///|http://)(path_to_rogueliki)/rogueliki.html#(API)/(MAP)/(PLAYER)/

API
  * "XMLRPC" - using WikiAPI.XMLRPC (required wiki.php, for web)
  * "TiddlyWiki.Files" - using WikiAPI.TiddlyWiki.Files (required TiddlyWiki.htm, for local)
  * default - read only using XMLHttpRequest

MAP / PLAYER
  * foo -> wiki/foo.js
  * foo:baa -> wiki/foo/baa.js
  * ^Rogueliki.*** -> JSAN.use('Rogueliki.***') and new Rogueliki.***

example
  * rogueliki.html#TiddlyWiki.Files/map:test/player:test/

----
